{"tid":2151757,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚班狗狂攪記者發洩","createTime":"2020-08-11T14:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T14:29:31.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"00f89e1ccd21eb80f2a3216cc27028ecc08a4899","tid":2151757,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"【沙田和你 Sing 警截查記者】軍裝警員再度衝入新城市廣場，在商場中庭包圍市民及記者，十多名市民和沙田區議員被截查，最終被截查市民全遭發違反限聚令告票。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳媒聯絡隊警員向在封鎖區的記者聲稱要核實傳媒身份及登記資料，要證實為「正式記者」，才可以在封鎖區外「進行專業、宏觀、多角度紀錄」，又指不希望假記者滲入真正記者群，妨礙真正記者的工作。<br />\n<br />\n封鎖區內起初只有兩名警員負責登記，進度緩慢。記者不滿，警員則回應「如果想快啲唔需要阻礙我哋同事工作」。有警員之後表示主流媒體可以先離開，之後指向《立場新聞》記者容許離開。<br />\n<br />\n整個截查記者的行動約半小時，期間再有軍裝警衝上商場上層追截，記者無辦法跟進。有警員要求個別記者證實自己為受薪員工方獲離開。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3349949848423945/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3349949848423945%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FlScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=2787d3f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3349949848423945/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"afb8673c6857e1145a53da2d5ae0c264c6f5168e","tid":2151757,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3349907341761529/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3349907341761529%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FlScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=5386b088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3349907341761529/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【旺角】記者被警推撞、壓倒地上<br />\n<br />\n晚上 9 時許，多名警員在朗豪坊外往彌敦道推進，有警員從馬路將一名記者推上行人路，亦有記者被壓倒在地上。警員指，現場人士或違犯限聚令，要求現場登記多名記者資料。另有多名途人被截查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/117282139_3349907345094862_5054344561277405509_n.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=A0NhUeX5d14AX_AYqHQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=a9febb7dbbc216dda4c520fe077a8836&amp;oe=5F599720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F117282139_3349907345094862_5054344561277405509_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DA0NhUeX5d14AX_AYqHQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3Da9febb7dbbc216dda4c520fe077a8836%26oe%3D5F599720&h=4ab87561&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"593c9d6f39d663215e12b331a22d100fc4972fd1","tid":2151757,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"警甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發脾氣話俾人zoom 撚有人想zoom佢咩 大大粒眼屎 博升職搵其他機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62aa003727600e3c77c9c9cbaace4c84cd9885f5","tid":2151757,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T14:27:55.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位巴絲幫手backup 啲片同相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最好包括直播 記住backup係保障你地 仲有好人好事都可以backup用作宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbackup片:  <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BAdzqffofRavFML57\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBAdzqffofRavFML57&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9FlScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=fde92ec4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BAdzqffofRavFML57</a><br />\n<br />\n睇片: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gBi8N70aMppNKcUgXcD2g1nBb1EUINfYTnUn4yrGGVQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1gBi8N70aMppNKcUg